---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout />
<div class="hero bg-base-200 min-h-screen">
  <div class="hero-content flex-col md:flex-row-reverse">
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      fill="currentColor"
      class="bi bi-file-bar-graph-fill shrink-0 w-36 h-36 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 lg:w-80 lg:h-80"
      viewBox="0 0 16 16"
    >
      <path
        d="M12 0H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2m-2 11.5v-6a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v6a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5m-2.5.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v4a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5zm-3 0a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-2a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v2a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5z"
      ></path>
    </svg>
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Mission</h1>
      <p class="py-6">
        We aim to provide people with a super easy way to view how much cash
        they may need each day after taking into account expenses and income.
      </p>
      <p class="py-2">
        It can be difficult to keep track of multiple credit card statements,
        Utilities, Mortgages, etc. A tool that can let you visualize when those
        expenses will come and when your paychecks come (or other income) is
        handy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="hero bg-base-300 min-h-screen">
  <div class="hero-content flex-col md:flex-row">
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      fill="currentColor"
      class="bi bi-shield-shaded shrink-0 w-36 h-36 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 lg:w-96 lg:h-96"
      viewBox="0 0 16 16"
    >
      <path
        fill-rule="evenodd"
        d="M8 14.933a1 1 0 0 0 .1-.025q.114-.034.294-.118c.24-.113.547-.29.893-.533a10.7 10.7 0 0 0 2.287-2.233c1.527-1.997 2.807-5.031 2.253-9.188a.48.48 0 0 0-.328-.39c-.651-.213-1.75-.56-2.837-.855C9.552 1.29 8.531 1.067 8 1.067zM5.072.56C6.157.265 7.31 0 8 0s1.843.265 2.928.56c1.11.3 2.229.655 2.887.87a1.54 1.54 0 0 1 1.044 1.262c.596 4.477-.787 7.795-2.465 9.99a11.8 11.8 0 0 1-2.517 2.453 7 7 0 0 1-1.048.625c-.28.132-.581.24-.829.24s-.548-.108-.829-.24a7 7 0 0 1-1.048-.625 11.8 11.8 0 0 1-2.517-2.453C1.928 10.487.545 7.169 1.141 2.692A1.54 1.54 0 0 1 2.185 1.43 63 63 0 0 1 5.072.56"
      ></path>
    </svg>
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Privacy</h1>
      <p class="py-6">
        We also prioritize privacy. It can always be risky and scary to provide
        your financial information to a company or website. We take privacy
        seriously which is why the data you add to this site will never leave
        this site. We use your browser's local storage and the code on the
        browser to show you what you want to see but it never comes back to any
        server. You can rest assured that we will never know if youre a
        billionaire or part of the class that is at the will and whimsy of those
        billionaires.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
